pt;&#10;     mso-border-alt:none windowtext 0cm;padding:0cm;mso-fareast-language:EN-IE\">Objectives      of the call<o:p></o:p></span></li>\r\n    <li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;&#10;     margin-left:-10.9pt;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo1\"><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;&#10;     font-family:inherit;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;border:none windowtext 1.0pt;&#10;     mso-border-alt:none windowtext 0cm;padding:0cm;mso-fareast-language:EN-IE\">Eligibility      requirements</span><span style=\"mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;&#10;     border:none windowtext 1.0pt;mso-border-alt:none windowtext 0cm;&#10;     padding:0cm;mso-fareast-language:EN-IE\"><o:p></o:p></span></li>\r\n    <li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;&#10;     margin-left:-10.9pt;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo1\"><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;&#10;     font-family:inherit;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;border:none windowtext 1.0pt;&#10;     mso-border-alt:none windowtext 0cm;padding:0cm;mso-fareast-language:EN-IE\">Award      criteria</span><span style=\"mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;&#10;     border:none windowtext 1.0pt;mso-border-alt:none windowtext 0cm;&#10;     padding:0cm;mso-fareast-language:EN-IE\"><o:p></o:p></span></li>\r\n    <li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;&#10;     margin-left:-10.9pt;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo1\"><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;&#10;     font-family:inherit;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;border:none windowtext 1.0pt;&#10;     mso-border-alt:none windowtext 0cm;padding:0cm;mso-fareast-language:EN-IE\">Application      process</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif;&#10;     mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-fareast-language:EN-IE\"><o:p></o:p></span></li>\r\n    <li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;&#10;     margin-left:-10.9pt;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo1\"><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;&#10;     font-family:inherit;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;border:none windowtext 1.0pt;&#10;     mso-border-alt:none windowtext 0cm;padding:0cm;mso-fareast-language:EN-IE\">Detailed      budget table (lump-sum type 2).</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;&#10;     font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;&#10;     mso-fareast-language:EN-IE\"><o:p></o:p></span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>&nbsp;<span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:inherit;border:none windowtext 1.0pt;&#10;mso-border-alt:none windowtext 0cm;padding:0cm\">Hence, they can be valuable aids for preparation of your proposals.</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;&#10;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>"}], "budgetOverviewJSONItem": {"budgetTopicActionMap": {"3508025": [{"action": "CERV-2024-GE - CERV-LS CERV Lump Sum Grants", "plannedOpeningDate": "21 December 2023", "deadlineModel": "single-stage", "deadlineDates": ["09 April 2024"], "budgetYearMap": {"2024": 10100000}, "budgetTopicActionMap": {}}]}, "budgetYearsColumns": ["2024"]}, "description": "<SPAN class=\"topicdescriptionkind\">Scope</SPAN>:<p>The objective of the Call is to support, advance and implement comprehensive policies to promote women\u2019s full enjoyment of rights, gender equality, including work-life balance, equal pay between women and men, women\u2019s empowerment and gender mainstreaming.</p><p>More specifically, the call focusses on the following two priorities:</p><ol level=\"0\">  <li><strong>Tackling the root causes of the gender care gap by promoting a gender-transformative approach and challenging gender stereotypes</strong> with the aim to support promotion of family-friendly practices in companies encouraging the take up of the new rights under the Work-life Balance Directive by both women and men; prevention/protection against any form of unfavourable treatment and discrimination of women during and after pregnancy as well as of women and men who took family leave and flexible work arrangements; raising awareness of the value of care work by reflecting on the appreciation of skills needed for care work; and challenging gender stereotypes that perpetuate the traditional division of labour.</li><li><strong>Supporting the implementation of the provisions of the Pay Transparency Directive </strong>with the aim to foster Member States authorities responsible for implementation of the provision of the Pay Transparency Directive (possibly in cooperation with other public entities, private organisations or international organisations) in developing national guidance and/or tools for gender-sensitive job evaluation and classification systems and in raising awareness of this guidance and/or tools among employers and workers representatives in their respective countries.</li> </ol>\n", "conditions": "<p>&nbsp;<b><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif;&#10;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;color:black;mso-fareast-language:&#10;EN-GB\">1.&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></b><b style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight:normal\"><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif;mso-fareast-font-family:&#10;&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;color:#1F497D;mso-themecolor:text2;mso-fareast-language:EN-GB\">Eligible countries</span></b><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif;&#10;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;color:#1F497D;mso-themecolor:text2;&#10;mso-fareast-language:EN-GB\">:&nbsp;as described in the <a href=\"https://ec.europa.eu/info/funding-tenders/opportunities/docs/2021-2027/cerv/wp-call/2024/call-fiche_cerv-2024-ge_en.pdf\" target=\"_blank\">Call document</a>.</span><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif;mso-fareast-font-family:&#10;&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;color:black;mso-fareast-language:EN-GB\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\n<p><b style=\"text-indent: -18pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 9pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;\">2.&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></b><b style=\"text-indent: -18pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;font-family:&#10;&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;color:#1F497D;&#10;mso-themecolor:text2;mso-fareast-language:EN-GB\">Eligibility and admissibility conditions:</span></b><span style=\"text-indent: -18pt; font-size: 9pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(31, 73, 125);\"> as described in the <a href=\"https://ec.europa.eu/info/funding-tenders/opportunities/docs/2021-2027/cerv/wp-call/2024/call-fiche_cerv-2024-ge_en.pdf\" target=\"_blank\">Call document</a>.</span>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: bold; font-size: 9pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(31, 73, 125);\">3. Proposal page limits and layout:</span><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif;&#10;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;color:#1F497D;mso-themecolor:text2;&#10;mso-fareast-language:EN-GB\">&nbsp;Please refer to Part B of the <a href=\"https://ec.europa.eu/info/funding-tenders/opportunities/docs/2021-2027/cerv/temp-form/af/af_cerv_en.pdf\" target=\"_blank\">standard proposal template</a>.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\n<p><b><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif;&#10;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;color:#1F497D;mso-themecolor:text2;&#10;mso-fareast-language:EN-GB\">4.&nbsp; &nbsp;Evaluation</span></b><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif;mso-fareast-font-family:&#10;&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;color:#1F497D;mso-themecolor:text2;mso-fareast-language:EN-GB\"><br />\r\n<br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Evaluation criteria, scoring, threshold and process are described in the <a href=\"https://ec.europa.eu/info/funding-tenders/opportunities/docs/2021-2027/cerv/wp-call/2024/call-fiche_cerv-2024-ge_en.pdf\" target=\"_blank\">Call document</a>.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left:18.0pt;text-indent:-18.0pt;line-height:&#10;normal\"><b><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif;&#10;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;color:#1F497D;mso-themecolor:text2;&#10;mso-fareast-language:EN-GB\">5.&nbsp;&nbsp; Indicative timetable for evaluation and grant agreement:</span></b><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif;&#10;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;color:#1F497D;mso-themecolor:text2;&#10;mso-fareast-language:EN-GB\"> as described in the <a href=\"https://ec.europa.eu/info/funding-tenders/opportunities/docs/2021-2027/cerv/wp-call/2024/call-fiche_cerv-2024-ge_en.pdf\" target=\"_blank\">Call document.</a><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;&#10;line-height:normal\"><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif;&#10;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;color:#1F497D;mso-themecolor:text2;&#10;mso-fareast-language:EN-GB\">Opening for submission:&nbsp; &nbsp; 21 December 2023<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;line-height:&#10;normal\"><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif;mso-fareast-font-family:&#10;&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;color:#1F497D;mso-themecolor:text2;mso-fareast-language:EN-GB\">Deadline for submitting applications:&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 09 April 2024&nbsp; 17:00 (Brussels Time)<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;line-height:&#10;normal\"><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif;mso-fareast-font-family:&#10;&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;color:#1F497D;mso-themecolor:text2;mso-fareast-language:EN-GB\">Evaluation period:&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;April - September 2024<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;line-height:&#10;normal\"><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif;mso-fareast-font-family:&#10;&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;color:#1F497D;mso-themecolor:text2;mso-fareast-language:EN-GB\">Information to applicants:&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; September - October 2024<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;line-height:&#10;normal\"><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif;mso-fareast-font-family:&#10;&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;color:#1F497D;mso-themecolor:text2;mso-fareast-language:EN-GB\">Signature of grant agreement:&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; October - December 2024<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><b><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;&#10;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;&#10;color:#1F497D;mso-themecolor:text2;mso-fareast-language:EN-GB\">6.&nbsp;&nbsp; Proposal templates, guidance and model grant agreements (MGA):</span></b><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif;mso-fareast-font-family:&#10;&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;color:#1F497D;mso-themecolor:text2;mso-fareast-language:EN-GB\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:normal\"><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;&#10;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;&#10;color:#1F497D;mso-themecolor:text2;mso-fareast-language:EN-GB\"><a href=\"https://ec.europa.eu/info/funding-tenders/opportunities/docs/2021-2027/cerv/temp-form/af/af_cerv_en.pdf\" target=\"_blank\">Standard proposal template </a><br />\r\n<a href=\"https://ec.europa.eu/info/funding-tenders/opportunities/docs/2021-2027/cerv/wp-call/2024/call-fiche_cerv-2024-ge_en.pdf\" target=\"_blank\"> Call document</a><br />\r\n</span><a href=\"https://ec.europa.eu/info/funding-tenders/opportunities/docs/2021-2027/cerv/temp-form/af/detailed-budget-table_cerv-lsii_en.xlsm\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"font-family: Arial, sans-serif;\">Detailed Budget Table</a><span style=\"font-family: Arial, sans-serif;\">&nbsp;(the budget table can also be downloaded during submission)<br />\r\n</span><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;&#10;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;&#10;color:#1F497D;mso-themecolor:text2;mso-fareast-language:EN-GB\"><a href=\"https://ec.europa.eu/info/funding-tenders/opportunities/docs/2021-2027/common/guidance/om_en.pdf\" target=\"_blank\">Guide for applicants</a><br />\r\n<a href=\"https://ec.europa.eu/info/funding-tenders/opportunities/docs/2021-2027/common/agr-contr/ls-mga_en.pdf\" target=\"_blank\"> Mono/Multi-beneficiary Model Grant Agreement</a></span><br />\r\n<span style=\"font-size: 9pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; border: 1pt none windowtext; padding: 0cm;\"><a href=\"https://commission.europa.eu/system/files/2022-12/c_2022_8588_1_en_annexe_acte_autonome_cp_part1_v2.pdf\" target=\"_blank\">CERV 2023-2024 work programme<br />\r\n</a></span><span style=\"font-size: 9pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;\"> <span style=\"border:none windowtext 1.0pt;mso-border-alt:none windowtext 0cm;&#10;padding:0cm\"><a href=\"https://eur-lex.europa.eu/legal-content/EN/TXT/?uri=uriserv%3AOJ.L_.2021.156.01.0001.01.ENG&amp;toc=OJ%3AL%3A2021%3A156%3ATOC\" target=\"_blank\">Regulation establishing the CERV Programme</a></span><br />\r\n<span style=\"border:none windowtext 1.0pt;mso-border-alt:none windowtext 0cm;&#10;padding:0cm\"><a href=\"https://ec.europa.eu/info/funding-tenders/opportunities/docs/2021-2027/cerv/guidance/ls-decision_cerv_en.pdf\" target=\"_blank\">Decision authorising the use of lump sums for actions under the Citizens, Equality, Rights and Values Programme (2021-2027)</a></span><br />\r\n<span style=\"border:none windowtext 1.0pt;mso-border-alt:none windowtext 0cm;&#10;padding:0cm\"><a href=\"https://ec.europa.eu/info/funding-tenders/opportunities/docs/2021-2027/common/guidance/unit-cost-decision-travel_en.pdf\" target=\"_blank\">Decision on unit costs for travel and subsistence</a></span><br />\r\n<span style=\"border:none windowtext 1.0pt;mso-border-alt:none windowtext 0cm;&#10;padding:0cm\"><a href=\"https://ec.europa.eu/info/funding-tenders/opportunities/docs/2021-2027/common/guidance/unit-cost-decision-volunteers_en.pdf\" target=\"_blank\">Decision on unit costs for volunteers</a></span></span><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif;mso-fareast-font-family:&#10;&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-ansi-language:EN-IE;mso-fareast-language:EN-IE\"><o:p></o:p></span><br />\r\n<a href=\"https://ec.europa.eu/info/funding-tenders/opportunities/docs/2021-2027/common/guidance/how-to-manage-your-lump-sum-grants_en.pdf\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 9pt;\">Guidance: How to manage your lump-sum grant</a></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:normal\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:normal\"><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;&#10;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;&#10;color:#1F497D;mso-themecolor:text2;mso-fareast-language:EN-GB\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>", "supportInfo": "<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 9pt;\">Please carefully read all provisions of the Call document and get familiar with the proposal template and its annexes before the preparation of your application.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\">For help related to this call, please contact&nbsp;</span><a href=\"mailto:EC-CERV-CALLS@ec.europa.eu\" style=\"font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; font-size: 11pt;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 102, 255);\">EC-CERV-CALLS@ec.europa.eu</span></a>&nbsp;<span style=\"font-size: 9pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;\">or the <a href=\"https://commission.europa.eu/system/files/2023-08/CERV%20Contact%20Points%203%20AUG%202023.pdf\" target=\"_blank\">CERV National Contact Point</a>&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-size: 9pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;\">of your country, if established.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span class=\"MsoHyperlink\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 9pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: windowtext; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\"><a href=\"https://ec.europa.eu/info/funding-tenders/opportunities/portal/screen/support/faq;grantAndTendertype=1;categories=p_submission_eval;programme=null;actions=;keyword=;period=null\">Funding &amp; Tenders Portal FAQ</a></span><span lang=\"EN-GB\"> &nbsp;</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">&ndash; Submission of proposals</span><span lang=\"EN-GB\">.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\"><a href=\"https://ec.europa.eu/info/funding-tenders/opportunities/portal/screen/support/helpdesks/contact-form\">IT Helpdesk</a></span><span lang=\"EN-GB\"> </span><span lang=\"EN-US\">&ndash; Contact the IT helpdesk for questions such as forgotten passwords, access rights and roles, technical aspects of submission of proposals, etc.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><a href=\"https://webgate.ec.europa.eu/funding-tenders-opportunities/display/OM/Online+Manual\" target=\"_blank\">Online Manual</a> &ndash;&nbsp;Step-by-step online guide through the Portal processes from proposal preparation and submission to reporting on your on-going project. Valid for all 2021-2027 programmes.</p>", "sepTemplate": "<p>To access the Electronic Submission Service, please click on the submission-button next to the <strong>type of action</strong> and the <strong>type of model grant agreement</strong> that corresponds to your proposal. You will then be asked to confirm your choice, as it cannot be changed in the submission system. Upon confirmation, you will be linked to the correct entry point.</p>\r\n<p>To access existing draft proposals for this topic, please login to the Funding &amp; Tenders Portal and select the My Proposals page of the My Area section.</p>", "links": [], "additionalDossiers": [], "infoPackDossiers": [], "callDetailsJSONItem": {"latestInfos": [{"approvalDate": "Jul 18, 2024 3:43:12 PM", "lastChangeDate": "Jul 18, 2024 3:43:12 PM", "content": "<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>Call update flash info</strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong> CERV-2024-GE: Call for proposals to promote gender equality</strong></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Publication date:      21 November 2023<br />\r\nType of action:         CERV Project Grants<br />\r\nOpening date:          21 December 2023<br />\r\nSingle-stage<br />\r\nDeadline:                 09 April 2024 17:00:00<br />\r\nCall's budget:           10.100.000 EUR<br />\r\n<br />\r\nNumber of proposals submitted: 196<br />\r\nNumber of eligible proposals: 188<br />\r\n<br />\r\nThe results of the evaluation were communicated to the applicants via the Funding and Tenders Portal on 17 July 2024.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nSummary of the results:<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<strong><u>Priority 1 &ndash; Gender Care Gap:</u></strong></p>\r\n<p>&bull; Award a grant to 17 proposals for EUR 6,082,027.20  <br />\r\n&bull; Place 4 proposals on the reserve list for EUR 1,674,834.34 <br />\r\n&bull; Reject 89 proposals for lack of budget <br />\r\n&bull; Reject 67 proposals due to insufficient relevance and/or overall quality <br />\r\n&bull; Reject 5 proposals due to inadmissibility/ineligibility</p>\r\n<p><strong><u>Priority 2 &ndash; Pay Transparency Directive Implementation:</u></strong></p>\r\n<p>&bull; Award a grant to 8 proposals for EUR 3,844,320.31 <br />\r\n&bull; Place 0 proposals on the reserve list <br />\r\n&bull; Reject 0 proposals for lack of budget <br />\r\n&bull; Reject 3 proposals due to insufficient relevance and/or quality <br />\r\n&bull; Reject 3 proposals due to inadmissibility/ineligibility </p>"}, {"approvalDate": "Feb 9, 2024 4:12:28 PM", "lastChangeDate": "Feb 9, 2024 4:12:28 PM", "content": "The submission session is now available for: CERV-2024-GE(CERV-LS)"}, {"approvalDate": "Dec 21, 2023 3:53:12 PM", "lastChangeDate": "Dec 21, 2023 3:53:12 PM", "content": "<p style=\"background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:&#10;&quot;inherit&quot;,serif;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;color:#333333;border:none windowtext 1.0pt;&#10;mso-border-alt:none windowtext 0cm;padding:0cm\">INFORMATION SESSION:</span></strong><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:&quot;inherit&quot;,serif;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;&#10;color:#333333\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:&quot;inherit&quot;,serif;&#10;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;color:#333333\">Join us online to know more about the call for proposals to promote gender equality (CERV-2024-GE).<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"background-image: initial; ba